description:
KLM Houses

Forget about the crumpled notes - download this app to store all your collected KLM houses. This app contains all miniature houses and provides, amongst others, the following functionalities:
- A scanner to find your house easy and fast;
- An overview, including image gallery, of all houses;
- Add notes so you can store every fond memory about the houses;
- Have duplicates? Keep track of how many houses you own;
- Read all about the history of all the houses;
- Find the location of the houses on Google Maps!
